snippet: Rabbi Barry Freundel, the spiritual leader of Kesher Israel, an influential Orthodox congregation, on Wednesday pleaded not guilty to six counts of misdemeanor voyeurism.
abstract: Rabbi Barry Freundel, spiritual leader of Kesher Israel, prominent Washington synagogue, pleads not guilty to six counts of misdemeanor voyeurism.
